    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >释放你内心的恶魔，抢先体验《凶兽》这款残酷非常的回合制战术RPG游戏。作为False Prophet的首发作品，《凶兽》通过一个游走在道德边缘、有血有肉的主角人物，重新定义无网格的回合制战术类游戏，如何作战由玩家自己来决定，在战场上以最有效的战略、最直接的方式打败敌人。当然了，你并不会孤身作战，忠诚的盟友将是你最有力的战队，人人身怀不同的技巧与能力。但你也将面临艰难的选择，到底是一同联手并肩作战还是吞噬他们来强化你的凶兽能力？游戏目前提供抢先体验版，False Prophet将听取各位玩家的反馈，致力于让《凶兽》成为一款出色的游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深刻而丰富的故事线</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145630/extras/1462498196c8dd6f12e21688f7e1845e.poster.avif?t=1743422888\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145630/extras/1462498196c8dd6f12e21688f7e1845e.webm?t=1743422888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>在奥斯曼帝国经历了长达十年的奴役苦难之后，一个即将被人遗忘的老兵终于回到喀尔巴阡山的故乡。然而这片土地早已被自诩为神的疯王统治，除了敌军的大肆毁坏还有无情的瘟疫入侵。他所热爱和珍视的一切大多已经荡然无存，剩下的也是物是人非。除了一队忠诚的士兵和结束瘟疫的神圣使命，他已是一无所有。要如何面对数量众多的敌人并战胜内心的恶魔？只能靠你不惜一切代价地帮助他完成任务！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的凶兽系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145630/extras/f3ad33d0a2c180c34fe6b97a8ce51412.poster.avif?t=1743422888\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145630/extras/f3ad33d0a2c180c34fe6b97a8ce51412.webm?t=1743422888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>锤炼或驱逐你内心的凶兽——由你决定。疯狂值系统将促使你在战斗时做出艰难的道德选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >黑暗时代的极致疯狂</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145630/extras/29a47dce579670d9396d0266a66148a9.poster.avif?t=1743422888\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145630/extras/29a47dce579670d9396d0266a66148a9.webm?t=1743422888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>受喀尔巴阡山传说的启发，这是一个氛围浓厚、故事丰富却又阴郁黑暗的世界。除了邪恶，你别无选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >利用远程武器缩小差距</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145630/extras/894d803cce43f8b453ba071afdc786d2.poster.avif?t=1743422888\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145630/extras/894d803cce43f8b453ba071afdc786d2.webm?t=1743422888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>在快节奏、无网格的回合制战术战斗中指挥你的小队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >残酷的近战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145630/extras/6cfa432041bb14018dee03b55432675a.poster.avif?t=1743422888\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145630/extras/6cfa432041bb14018dee03b55432675a.webm?t=1743422888\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>在紧张血腥的交锋中生存与前进。</p>",
